  "description": "systemd unit health for Linux hosts scraped by node_exporter: the count of failed units, the active/inactive breakdown, and a live table of exactly which units have failed and where. Answers \"is any service down on these hosts, and which one?\" rather than leaving you to SSH and run systemctl.",
